1 paid the one-star county market rate or the rate they charge privately paying
2 parents unless prohibited by subsection (f) of this section.Licensed child care
3 centers and homes, including religious sponsored child care facilities
4 operating pursuant to G.S. 110-106, that meet the minimum licensing
5 standards as set forth in G.S. 110-91, that are participating in the subsidized
